{"tid":1695342,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"對身邊的人多一點關心","createTime":"2019-11-05T14:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T15:09:43.000Z","uid":9096,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61440b5f0de36dbfd7da711d18b97b2390241bd9","tid":1695342,"uid":9096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日小弟收工就慶高彩烈咁翻屋企，點知一上巴士就訓著咗<br />\n一開眼已經過咗站<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到要洗多三十蚊坐的士翻屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知落車帶住耳機行翻屋企嘅途中，聽到有人係我背後大叫&rdquo;垃圾，死垃圾。&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我就回頭一望，見到一位中年嘅男人望住我，隨即大叫&rdquo;啤乜撚野啊啤&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又衝上黎作狀兇我，用佢胸前嘅袋胸襲我，並作出持續騷擾及跟蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其間個位中年又大叫又報稱自己有精神病，但係周圍嘅途人冇一個對柔弱嘅我伸出援手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，令我深感失望<br />\n唯有走入區議會辦士處尋求幫助，然後該男人隨即正常翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，徘徊咗一鄰之後就向隔離嘅紀律部隊宿舍移動係遠處觀察我。<br />\n成個過程擾攘大半個鐘，搞到我翻到屋企啲餸都凍哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家可以對身邊嘅人多一啲關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到需要幫助嘅人要伸出援手<br />\n<br />\n利申：帶咗口罩<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得1124一早去投票啊屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2581d4a0c5706c178b60043bb32204f7140374a7","tid":1695342,"uid":9096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8b4517b75ce83409a4684a41f32cb2303eb3e64","tid":1695342,"uid":9096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"保護身邊嘅人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dd01ccb5315c6bb2249c70526e8591e231e287","tid":1695342,"uid":9096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93882b108887ac6b2ca8dae6f1bac4cc4a43847","tid":1695342,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4d523bd8b17d75da62a0a0bfb5340ca5f7c8a0","tid":1695342,"uid":20809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"俾我遇到一定幫你拖，放心"},{"pid":"7156bac93d52b214a7e00196493b3bd973cfa8b8","tid":1695342,"uid":9096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee4d523bd8b17d75da62a0a0bfb5340ca5f7c8a0","tid":1695342,"uid":20809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"俾我遇到一定幫你拖，放心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:53:36.000Z","msg":"廢老邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a850db3a301f953799523cecec10f78f2a1c9b4","tid":1695342,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7156bac93d52b214a7e00196493b3bd973cfa8b8","tid":1695342,"uid":9096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee4d523bd8b17d75da62a0a0bfb5340ca5f7c8a0","tid":1695342,"uid":20809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"俾我遇到一定幫你拖，放心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:53:36.000Z","msg":"廢老邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"順利?"},{"pid":"116c843047f7cbc9a2f6b461b4f5de93d0bd5